```
###############################################################################
## Rapid Data Objects
###############################################################################
```

Rapid Data Objects (RDO) is a very lightweight ORM that requires NO-CONFIGURATION.

RDO is compatible with Java 6 and above.

```
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---- Prerequisites for Development
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
```

Before building with Ant ensure the following environment variables are set:
- WORK_HOME ...... the directory preceding the Mercurial depot
- STAGING_HOME ... a temporary directory for staging files
- HSQLDB_HOME .... installation directory of HSQLDB (to run end-to-end tests)

Optionally you can set the following environment variables:
- ANT_HOME ....... required by ANT
- JAVA_HOME ...... pointing to your Java 7 JDK directory
